title: Toddler Grease T-Birds Jacket Costume Child Thunderbirds Greaser Jacket
description: The Fun Costumes Child's Grease T-Bird Jacket Costume Is your toddler one tough little cookie? Does he yearn to join the big boys for some hot-rodding? Well, this exclusive Toddler T-Birds Jacket is designed to look just like the ones the T-Birds wear in the movie Grease, so your little guy will look as cool as a real hot-rodder! The only way they could be cuter if they found a gal-friend wearing one of our Toddler Pink Ladies jackets to recreate scenes of the movie!
